.TH "LIGHTNING-NODE-UTXO-LIST" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-node-utxo-list \- list on-chain UTXOs held by the node
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning node-utxo-list
.SH DESCRIPTION
Returns the list of on-chain outputs from
.B lightning-cli listfunds
with their status (confirmed, unconfirmed) and reservation flag.
Returns an empty array if the daemon is unreachable.
.PP
Output:
.nf
[{txid, output, amount_msat, status, reserved}]
.fi
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-node-onchain-balance (1),
.BR lightning-node-funds (1)
